    "terms.kicker": "Legal",
    "terms.title": "Terms of Service",
    "terms.updated": "Last updated: July 24, 2026",
    "terms.reviewNotice":
      "Prelaunch notice: qualified legal counsel must review and adapt these terms before production launch.",
    "terms.eligibility.title": "Eligibility",
    "terms.eligibility.text":
      "You must be legally able to enter agreements and provide accurate information to use Boatstead.",
    "terms.accounts.title": "Accounts",
    "terms.accounts.text":
      "You are responsible for your account, sign-in details and activity. Tell us promptly about unauthorized access.",
    "terms.platform.title": "Platform role",
    "terms.platform.text":
      "Boatstead only facilitates introductions between boat owners and sitters. Any sit arrangement is a contract between the owner and the sitter. Boatstead does not own vessels, employ members, supervise sits or become a party to those arrangements.",
    "terms.listings.title": "Listings and applications",
    "terms.listings.text":
      "Listings and applications must be accurate, current and complete. Members decide whether to enter a sit arrangement.",
    "terms.responsibilities.title": "User responsibilities",
    "terms.responsibilities.text":
      "Members must act lawfully, communicate honestly, follow written expectations and take reasonable care.",
    "terms.verification.title": "Verification",
    "terms.verification.text":
      "Checks can reduce risk but do not guarantee identity, conduct, qualifications, safety or suitability.",
    "terms.prohibited.title": "Prohibited conduct",
    "terms.prohibited.text":
      "Do not commit fraud, harassment, discrimination, unsafe acts, unauthorized access, illegal activity or platform misuse.",
    "terms.nonDiscrimination.title": "Non-discrimination",
    "terms.nonDiscrimination.text":
      "You may not discriminate against any member based on protected characteristics, including race, color, ethnicity, national origin, religion, sex, gender, gender identity, gender expression, sexual orientation, age, disability, marital status, or any other status protected by applicable law. Discrimination in listings, applications, messaging, selection decisions, or other use of Boatstead is prohibited.",
    "terms.payments.title": "Payments and fees",
    "terms.payments.text":
      "Boatstead currently charges no nightly fee. If paid features are introduced, applicable terms and prices will be shown first.",
    "terms.cancellations.title": "Cancellations",
    "terms.cancellations.text":
      "Members should agree cancellation plans in writing and communicate changes promptly to reduce harm and expense.",
    "terms.insurance.title": "Insurance",
    "terms.insurance.text":
      "Members are responsible for confirming suitable insurance. Boatstead does not provide vessel, travel or liability insurance.",
    "terms.damage.title": "Damage and claims",
    "terms.damage.text":
      "Any damage, theft or similar claim is primarily between the owner and the sitter. Document incidents promptly, preserve evidence and cooperate with the other party, marinas, insurers and authorities.",
    "terms.intellectualProperty.title": "Intellectual property",
    "terms.intellectualProperty.text":
      "Boatstead content and branding are protected. You retain rights to your content and grant us permission to operate the service.",
    "terms.privacy.title": "Privacy",
    "terms.privacy.text":
      "Personal information must be handled responsibly. A production privacy notice will describe collection, use, retention and rights.",
    "terms.termination.title": "Suspension and termination",
    "terms.termination.text":
      "We may restrict or end access to protect members, investigate concerns, enforce terms or comply with law.",
    "terms.disclaimers.title": "Disclaimers",
    "terms.disclaimers.text":
      "The prototype is provided as available without guarantees of uninterrupted operation, suitability, accuracy or outcomes.",
    "terms.liability.title": "Limitation of liability",
    "terms.liability.text":
      "To the extent permitted by law, Boatstead is not liable for damage, theft, loss, injury, travel disruption, property claims or any other outcome arising from arrangements between members. Members deal with each other at their own risk.",
    "terms.indemnity.title": "Indemnity",
    "terms.indemnity.text":
      "Where legally permitted, you agree to cover claims caused by your unlawful conduct, content or breach of these terms.",
    "terms.disputes.title": "Disputes and governing law",
    "terms.disputes.text":
      "The production terms must specify a company entity, jurisdiction, governing law and dispute process after legal review.",
    "terms.changes.title": "Changes to these terms",
    "terms.changes.text":
      "We may update these terms and will provide appropriate notice before material changes take effect.",
    "terms.contact.title": "Contact and support",
    "terms.contact.text":
      "Use the Support page for questions. Do not rely on Boatstead support for emergency response.",
