      "Read references, reviews and experience carefully. Ask follow-up questions about gaps or unfamiliar systems.",
    "safety.video.title": "Meet by video",
    "safety.video.text":
      "Arrange a video call, involve everyone who will stay aboard and walk through the vessel live when practical.",
